title: 20 of the Craziest Videos from the #BookBagChallenge
text:
20 of the Craziest Videos from the #BookBagChallenge Tweet Posted: Tue, 2/7/2017 - 11:42pm by Brendan 
The #BookBagChallenge (sometimes called the #BackPackChallenge) is actually from way back in December 2016, but it’s having a comeback in the last day after tweet-stealing account @girlposts reposted one of the better videos. Since the challenge wasn’t incredibly popular the first time, and people are making new videos again, it seemed like a perfect time to cover some of the best examples. 
To do the #BookBagChallenge, all you have to do is run through a gauntlet of classmates who are all throwing their backpacks at you. If it sounds like one of the stupidest challenges yet , that’s because it IS. 
Don’t try this at home and don’t ask people to hit you in the head with a bag of books. You'll get a concussion, you dummies. 1. 
— yung bull$❤️ (@jayygotpesos) December 9, 2016 2.
